<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head'); %>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <%- include('../partials/sellerHeader'); %>
</header>

<main>
    <div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="1"></li>
          <li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>
        <div id="divCarousel" class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img class="d-block w-100 h-80" src="https://files.porsche.com/filestore/image/multimedia/none/po-416-r4-detail-audioandcommunication-bose-xle/zoom/36a1e351-3ff6-11e3-bd76-001a64c55f5c;s3/porsche-zoom.jpg" alt="First slide">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-block">
                <h5>Ofertas</h5>
                <p>Aprovecha hasta un 20% de descuento</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100 justify-center" src="https://photos.enjoei.com.br/public/1200x1200/czM6Ly9waG90b3MuZW5qb2VpLmNvbS5ici9wcm9kdWN0cy85ODE5NTMwLzg3MmJlMDY3ZGM2ZDRhY2M0NjkxMjgzOTMwN2U5NWY5LmpwZw" alt="Second slide">
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img class="d-block w-100" src="https://blog.br.playstation.com/tachyon/sites/4/2020/04/FEAT_DS-1.jpg" alt="Third slide">
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-light ">
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
            <img class="mt-5"src="/images/logo1.svg" width="100" height="100" alt="">
        </div>
        <div class="container text-center text-secondary">
            <p>EcaStore es una plataforma en la que puedes 
                publicar uno o más negocios con el propósito de que tengan un mayor alcance. 
                ¡No lo dudes más y<br> publica tu primer negocio! verás como tus ventas se 
                incrementarán al instante.  
            </p>        
        </div>
        <div id="addProduct" class="mt-2 mb-5 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <button class="btn btn-primary" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#registerStore" data-whatever="@mdo"><i class="bi bi-plus"></i>Publicar Negocio</button>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white">
            <br>
            <br>
            <h4 class="ml-5 mb-5">Explora la variedad de negocios de otros e inspírate a mejorar los tuyos.</h3>
            <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center bg-white">
                <% stores.forEach(function(store) { %>
                    <div class="card mr-5 mb-5" style="width: 18rem;">
                        <img class="card-img-top" src="/images/<%= store.img %>" alt="Card image cap">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title"><strong><%= store.name %></strong></h5>
                            <p class="card-text"><%= store.description %></p>
                            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/users/OtherSellersStoreProducts/<%= store.id %>">Ver productos</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            </div>
        </div>
        
    </div>
</main>

<!--Modal-->
<div class="modal fade" id="registerStore" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="exampleModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
        <div class="modal-header">
            <h5 class="modal-title" id="exampleModalLabel">Publica tu negocio</h5>
            <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
            <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <form class="" onsubmit='return registerStore(this, event);' method='post'>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="recipient-name" class="col-form-label">Nombre del Negocio*</label>
                    <input id="name" type="text" class="form-control" id="recipient-name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlSelect1">Categoría*</label>
                    <select id="category" class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlSelect1">
                        <option value="1">Cafetería</option>
                        <option value="2">Carnicería</option>
                        <option value="3">Cremería</option>
                        <option value="4">Dulceria</option>
                        <option value="5">Ferretería</option>
                        <option value="6">Florería</option>
                        <option value="7">Fonda</option>
                        <option value="8">Papelería</option>
                        <option value="9">Pollería</option>
                        <option value="10">Tienda de Abarrotes</option>
                        <option value="11">Tlapalería</option>
                        <option value="12">Tortillería</option>
                        <option value="13">Verdulería</option>
                        <option value="14">Vinatería</option>                    
                        <option value="15">Otro</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="message-text" class="col-form-label">Descripción*</label>
                    <textarea id="description" class="form-control" id="message-text"></textarea>
                    <small class="form-text text-muted">10-150 palabras</small>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="exampleFormControlFile1">Foto*</label>
                    <div class="custom-file">
                        <input id="img" type="file" class="custom-file-input" id="validatedCustomFile">
                        <label class="custom-file-label" for="validatedCustomFile">Elija una foto...</label>
                        <div class="invalid-feedback">Debe seleccionar una foto</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="recipient-name" class="col-form-label">Telefono de Contacto*</label>
                    <input id="phone" type="text" class="form-control" id="recipient-name">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="recipient-name" class="col-form-label">Email de Contacto*</label>
                    <input id="email" type="text" class="form-control" id="recipient-name">
                </div>
                <!-- Dirección -->
                <div class="form-row">
                    <div class="col form-group">
                      <label for="state">Estado*</label>
                      <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" id="state" required readonly>
                        <option>Estado de México</option>
                      </select>
                    </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                    <div class="col form-group">
                      <label>Region</label>
                      <input id="region" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="" >
                      <small class="form-text text-muted"></small>
                    </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                    </div> <!-- form-row end.// -->
                    <div class="form-row">
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label for="state">Municipio</label>
                            <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" id="state" required readonly>
                                <option>Ecatepec de Morelos</option>
                            </select>
                        </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label for="state">Colonia</label>
                            <select class="custom-select d-block w-100" id="state" required readonly>
                                <option>San Cristobal Centro</option>
                            </select>
                        </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label>Calle</label>
                            <input id="street" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="" >
                            <small class="form-text text-muted"></small>
                        </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-row">
                        
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label>Núm. Exterior*</label>
                            <input id="numExt" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="" >
                            <small class="form-text text-muted"></small>
                        </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label>Núm. Interior</label>
                            <input id="numInt" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="" >
                            <small class="form-text text-muted"></small>
                        </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                        <div class="col form-group">
                            <label>CP</label>
                            <input id="cp" type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="" value="55000" readonly >
                            <small class="form-text text-muted"></small>
                        </div> <!-- form-group end.// -->
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message-text" class="col-form-label">Descripción de Referencia*</label>
                        <textarea id="descriptionReference" class="form-control" id="message-text"></textarea>
                        <small class="form-text text-muted">10-150 palabras</small>
                    </div>
                </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <div class="addProduct">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Cancelar</button>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Publicar Negocio</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>


<footer>
    <%- include('../partials/footerSeller'); %>
</footer>
</body>
</html>